# Journals without an explicit robot/AI policy (as of 2025-07-26)

These journals have no explicit robot/AI policy noted in the stored guideline summaries and quick manual checks; please verify against the current author instructions before submission.

- Science (AAAS) — Author guidelines: https://www.science.org/content/page/science-information-authors
- Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences (PNAS) — Author guidelines: https://www.pnas.org/page/authors
- Journal of Cognitive Neuroscience (JoCN) — Submission guidelines: https://direct.mit.edu/jocn/pages/submission-guidelines
- Nature — Author formatting guide: https://www.nature.com/nature/for-authors/formatting-guide
- Nature Neuroscience — Author guidelines: https://www.nature.com/neuro/for-authors
- Journal of Neuroscience — Manuscript preparation: https://www.jneurosci.org/content/preparing-manuscript
- eLife — Author guide: https://reviewer.elifesciences.org/author-guide/full
- PLOS Biology — Submission guidelines: https://journals.plos.org/plosbiology/s/submission-guidelines
- PLOS ONE — Submission guidelines: https://journals.plos.org/plosone/s/submission-guidelines
- Current Biology — Author guidelines: https://www.cell.com/current-biology/authors
